  "criteria.atmosphere_desc": "How would you describe the overall feeling in the classroom? Consider whether the environment feels safe, inclusive, and conducive to learning, where students feel comfortable participating and asking questions.",
  "criteria.lesson_focus_desc": "How clear and purposeful are the lessons? Consider whether each class has a clear objective, stays on track, and whether you understand what you are supposed to learn by the end.",
  "criteria.interaction_desc": "How much opportunity is there for interaction and collaboration? Consider whether lessons include discussion, group work, peer learning, and whether the teacher encourages students to engage with each other.",
  "criteria.agency_desc": "How much choice and ownership do you have in your learning? Consider whether you can make decisions about how you learn, explore topics that interest you, and take initiative in class.",
  "criteria.rigour_desc": "How intellectually challenging are the lessons? Consider whether the teacher pushes you to think deeply, sets high expectations, and provides work that stretches your abilities appropriately.",
  "criteria.practical_app_desc": "How well does the teacher connect theory to practical application within class? Consider whether lessons include hands-on activities, experiments, case studies, or real examples that help you understand concepts.",
  "criteria.real_life_app_desc": "How well does the teacher connect what you learn to the real world? Consider whether you understand why the material matters and how it applies outside the classroom.",
  "criteria.preparedness_desc": "How well-prepared is the teacher for each class? Consider whether lessons are organized, materials are ready, and the teacher has a clear plan, or whether class time often feels improvised or wasted.",
  "criteria.feedback_qual_desc": "How useful and timely is the feedback you receive? Consider whether the teacher gives constructive comments on your work, explains how to improve, and returns assessments in a reasonable timeframe.",
  "criteria.subject_knowledge_desc": "How well does the teacher know their subject? Consider whether they can answer questions confidently, explain concepts in multiple ways, and demonstrate deep understanding of the material.",
  "criteria.approachability_desc": "How approachable and available is the teacher? Consider whether you feel comfortable asking questions, seeking help after class, and whether the teacher is welcoming and responsive.",
  "criteria.varied_methods_desc": "How varied are the teaching methods used? Consider whether lessons include a mix of lectures, discussions, group work, multimedia, and hands-on activities, and whether the teacher adapts to different learning styles.",
  "criteria.engaging_content_desc": "How well does the teacher balance engaging content with exam preparation? Consider whether classes go beyond just preparing for tests and whether the teacher makes the subject genuinely interesting to learn.",
